quran[30]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,46,"Àti pé àwa máa ń pe Ọjọ́ ẹ̀san ní irọ́"
  74,47,"títí ikú fi dé bá wa.”"
  74,48,"Ìpẹ̀ àwọn olùṣìpẹ̀ kò sì níí ṣe wọ́n ní àǹfààní."
  77,34,"Ègbé ni ní ọjọ́ yẹn fún àwọn olùpe-òdodo-nírọ́"
  77,35,"Èyí ni ọjọ́ tí wọn kò níí sọ̀rọ̀."
  77,36,"A kò sì níí yọ̀ǹda (ọ̀rọ̀ sísọ) fún wọn, áḿbọ̀sìbọ́sí pé wọ́n yóò mú àwáwí wá."
  78,31,"Dájúdájú ìgbàlà wà fún àwọn olùbẹ̀rù (Allāhu)."
  78,32,"Àwọn ọgbà oko àti èso àjàrà,"
  78,33,"àti àwọn ọlọ́mọge, tí wọn kò júra wọn lọ lọ́jọ́-orí,"
  79,25,"Nítorí náà, Allāhu gbá a mú pẹ̀lú ìyà ìkẹ́yìn àti àkọ́kọ́ (nípa ọ̀rọ̀ ẹnu rẹ̀ ìkẹ́yìn yìí àti àkọ́kọ́).1 {1}",footnotes:1:Ọ̀rọ̀ àkọ́kọ́ náà nìyí, Fir‘aon wí pé: “Ẹ̀yin ìjòyè, èmi kò mọ̀ pé ọlọ́hun kan tún wà lẹ́yìn mi!” Sūrah al-Ƙọsọs;  28:38
  79,26,"Dájúdájú àríwòye wà nínú ìyẹn fún ẹni tó ń páyà (Allāhu)."
  79,27,"Ṣé ẹ̀yin lẹ lágbára jùlọ ní ìṣẹ̀dá ni tàbí sánmọ̀ tí Allāhu mọ?"
  80,22,"Lẹ́yìn náà, nígbà tí Allāhu bá fẹ́, Ó máa gbé e dìde."
  80,23,"Rárá o! Ènìyàn kò tí ì ṣe n̄ǹkan tí Allāhu pa láṣẹ fún un."
  80,24,"Nítorí náà, kí ènìyàn wòye sí oúnjẹ rẹ̀."
  81,19,"Dájúdájú (al-Ƙur’ān) ni ọ̀rọ̀ (tí A fi rán Jibrīl) Òjíṣẹ́, alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé,1 {1}",footnotes:1:Wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Hāƙƙọh;  69:40.
  81,20,"alágbára, ẹni pàtàkì ní ọ̀dọ̀ Ẹni t’Ó ni Ìtẹ́-ọlá,"
  81,21,"ẹni tí wọ́n ń tẹ̀lé àṣẹ rẹ̀ níbẹ̀ yẹn (nínú sánmọ̀), olùfọkàntán."
  82,13,"Dájúdájú àwọn ẹni rere yóò kúkú wà nínú ìgbádùn."
  82,14,"Dájúdájú àwọn ẹni ibi yó sì kúkú wà nínú iná Jẹhīm."
  82,15,"Wọn yóò wọ inú rẹ̀ ní Ọjọ́ ẹ̀san."
  83,10,"Ní ọjọ́ yẹn, ègbé ni fún àwọn olùpe-òdodo- nírọ́,"
  83,11,"àwọn tó ń pe Ọjọ́ ẹ̀san ní irọ́."
  83,12,"Kò sì sí ẹni tó ń pè é ní irọ́ àyàfi gbogbo alákọyọ, ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀."
  84,7,"Nítorí náà, ní ti ẹni tí wọ́n bá fún ní ìwé iṣẹ́ rẹ̀ ní ọwọ́ ọ̀tún rẹ̀,"
  84,8,"láìpẹ́ A máa ṣe ìṣírò-iṣẹ́ (rẹ̀) ní ìṣírò ìrọ̀rùn."
  84,9,"Ó sì máa padà sí ọ̀dọ̀ àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀ (nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra) lẹ́ni ìdùnnú."
  85,4,"A ṣẹ́bi lé àwọn tó gbẹ́ kòtò (iná),"
  85,5,"(ìyẹn) iná tí wọ́n ń fi igi kò (nínú kòtò)."
  85,6,"(Rántí) nígbà tí wọ́n jókòó sí ìtòsí rẹ̀."